Hassan Johnson https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hassan_Johnson 0 Hassan "Iniko" Johnson (born October 3, 1977) is an American actor, model and film producer from Brooklyn, New York. His most notable performance was in the HBO program The Wire as Roland "Wee-Bey" Brice.
